data.name: Vennominon the King of Poisonous Snakes
data.desc: Cannot be Special Summoned by another Effect Monster's effect. This card is unaffected by "Venom Swamp". This card gains 500 ATK for each Reptile-Type monster in your Graveyard. When this card is destroyed by battle and sent to the Graveyard: You can banish 1 other Reptile-Type monster from your Graveyard; Special Summon this card.

card_sets.set_name: Legendary Collection 2: The Duel Academy Years Mega Pack
